#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an9.25"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.25:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.25:0.2"
msgid "3. Sattāvāsavagga "
msgstr "3. Abodes of Sentient Beings "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 25. Paññāsutta → paññāparicitasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an9.25:0.3"
msgid "25. Paññāsutta "
msgstr "25. Consolidated by Wisdom "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.402, sc1
msgctxt "an9.25:1.1"
msgid "“Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno paññāya cittaṃ suparicitaṃ hoti, tassetaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno kallaṃ vacanāya: "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when a mendicant’s mind has been well consolidated with wisdom it’s appropriate for them to say: "

msgctxt "an9.25:1.2"
msgid "‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānāmī’ti. "
msgstr "‘I understand: “Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.”’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an9.25:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno paññāya cittaṃ suparicitaṃ hoti? "
msgstr "And how is a mendicant’s mind well consolidated with wisdom? "

msgctxt "an9.25:2.2"
msgid "‘Vītarāgaṃ me cittan’ti paññāya cittaṃ suparicitaṃ hoti; "
msgstr "The mind is well consolidated with wisdom when they know: ‘My mind is without greed.’ "

msgctxt "an9.25:2.3"
msgid "‘vītadosaṃ me cittan’ti paññāya cittaṃ suparicitaṃ hoti; "
msgstr "… ‘My mind is without hate.’ "

msgctxt "an9.25:2.4"
msgid "‘vītamohaṃ me cittan’ti paññāya cittaṃ suparicitaṃ hoti; "
msgstr "… ‘My mind is without delusion.’ "

msgctxt "an9.25:2.5"
msgid "‘asarāgadhammaṃ me cittan’ti paññāya cittaṃ suparicitaṃ hoti; "
msgstr "… ‘My mind is not liable to become greedy.’ "

msgctxt "an9.25:2.6"
msgid "‘asadosadhammaṃ me cittan’ti paññāya cittaṃ suparicitaṃ hoti; "
msgstr "… ‘My mind is not liable to become hateful.’ "

msgctxt "an9.25:2.7"
msgid "‘asamohadhammaṃ me cittan’ti paññāya cittaṃ suparicitaṃ hoti; "
msgstr "… ‘My mind is not liable to become deluded.’ "

msgctxt "an9.25:2.8"
msgid "‘anāvattidhammaṃ me cittaṃ kāmabhavāyā’ti paññāya cittaṃ suparicitaṃ hoti; "
msgstr "… ‘My mind is not liable to return to rebirth in the sensual realm.’ "

msgctxt "an9.25:2.9"
msgid "‘anāvattidhammaṃ me cittaṃ rūpabhavāyā’ti paññāya cittaṃ suparicitaṃ hoti; "
msgstr "… ‘My mind is not liable to return to rebirth in the realm of luminous form.’ "

msgctxt "an9.25:2.10"
msgid "‘anāvattidhammaṃ me cittaṃ arūpabhavāyā’ti paññāya cittaṃ suparicitaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "… ‘My mind is not liable to return to rebirth in the formless realm.’ "

msgctxt "an9.25:2.11"
msgid "Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno paññāya cittaṃ suparicitaṃ hoti, tassetaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno kallaṃ vacanāya: "
msgstr "When a mendicant’s mind has been well consolidated with wisdom it’s appropriate for them to say: "

msgctxt "an9.25:2.12"
msgid "‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānāmī’”ti. "
msgstr "‘I understand: “Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.”’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.25:2.13"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

